    <p>HANNITY: He's playing games.</p>
    <p>ASSANGE: He's playing games.</p>
    <p>HANNITY: He's dishonest - fair? Is he lying to the American people?</p>
    <p>ASSANGE: He's acting like a lawyer instead of being honest.</p>
    <p>WELNA: And Trump weighed in again today on this brouhaha with another tweet that reads, quote, "the dishonest media like saying that I am in agreement with Julian Assange - wrong. I simply state what he states."</p>
