    <p>POWER: This is not what you're used to.</p>
    <p>UNIDENTIFIED MAN: No, it's very hot in Tonga.</p>
    <p>KELEMEN: Ambassador Power says the goal of her courtesy calls was to show respect and curiosity. She believes that helps the U.S. gain allies in the United Nations. In Tonga's case, she already knew the ambassador pretty well.</p>
