    <p>VARMETTE: We dump them here. Here's where we count them. We</p>
    <p>MANN: It's a bottle and can recycling shop on the outskirts of his tiny hometown, Crown Point, N.Y.</p>
    <p>VARMETTE: It takes a lot of bottles and cans to pay bills.</p>
